			<div class="book-header">
				<div class="vers-view-type">
					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200218035332/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Th/8095?vers_inline=1"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20200218035332im_/http://catholicbible.online/assets/img/para.jpg" alt=""/></a>					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200218035332/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Th/8095?comments_open=1"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20200218035332im_/http://catholicbible.online/assets/img/C-off.gif" alt=""/></a>				</div>
				<div class="bible-name">The Holy Bible – Knox Translation</div>
				<div class="book-name">The First Epistle of the Blessed Apostle Paul to the Thessalonians </div>
