					<div class="prev-chapter"></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 1</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200218035332/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/1_Th/8096">next &gt;</a></div>
